{
  "stem": "3855.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Each barracks-- each barrack might have had 300 to 400 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three layers of bunk beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were all, in my barrack, all Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The way I understood it, towards the end of the camp-- homosexuals, political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There no-- there were no women at the time in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did have, as I mentioned before, a gentile barrack supervisor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Inspections were done by uniformed SS men periodically for cleanliness, staying at attention, toothbrush inspection.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And our contact was strictly within our own barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were-- what, when we were ordered to march, we'd march in groups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When we ate, we ate-- or rather they, I was the food carrier-- ate at the same standing-up position at that table or crouching down somewheres.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So each barrack had its own sanitary facilities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was very little contact between barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But within the barrack-- we had, unfortunately, an epileptic in our barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was a miserable situation at times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we made friends within our barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were other students.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were some people that I knew, merchants my father had done business with, two brothers, [NON-ENGLISH], a Hungarian name, probably at one time [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was a gentleman that lived in our building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was in the carpentry business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As the winter progressed, we were issued some tattered military overcoats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I finally was called out, I gave him my overcoat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He wasn't issued one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was totally random and haphazard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The only punishment I ever received was I was standing in line to purchase these sardines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I had my hand in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "An SS man kicked me in my behind with such force that I really almost collapsed and shouted, take your hand out!",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
